latestPosts.caption:
Any resemblance to real-life events, people or life choices is 100% intentional🤡

#funny #hyroxworld #athletelife #medal #fypage #funnyreel #sports

On 6th May, a few days after my first HYROX, I got invited to the World Championships.

Of course, I didn’t feel ready. I didn’t feel worthy.

But my people at @breathestudio.in saw something I couldn’t yet see in myself💫

They rallied behind me, gave me strength, and reminded me that I belong. From questioning whether I deserved to be there to representing India on the world stage, this journey has been nothing short of a dream.

To my @breathestudio.in family💖💪

You carried me forward. What started as a personal challenge has become something so much bigger. Thank you for backing me when I didn’t know how to back myself.

🇮🇳And now here I am.

On the brink of representing India on a global stage and carrying your voices, your faith, and your fire with me.

To say thank you feels too small.
But still— thank you.
For lifting me to a place I never knew I could reach.

So glad @hyroxindia made it to Mumbai and now in Delhi soon📍

And finally
Biggest shout out to @subtle.strength @rashiwadhera_ @pdoshi_99 

Thank you. You guys made this real🤍

#hyroxworld #hyrox #worldchampionships #hyroxtraining
